text-Emerald400\">Skills.</div>\r\n		<svg class=\"absolute w-8 h-20 top-0 md:top-4 right-4 md:right-10 svg-inherit\">\r\n			<use xlink:href=\"#glyph-hoops\"></use>\r\n		</svg>\r\n				\r\n		[[picture class=\"lazyload object-scale-down mx-auto h-60 md:h-80 lg:h-96\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/Essential/Cutouts/Lizzie_Kettlebell.png\" alt=\"Lizzy lifts a kettlebell.\"]]\r\n				\r\n		<div class=\"text-3xl pt-2 border-t-2 pb-6\">Qualified</div>\r\n		<div class=\"flex items-stretch\">\r\n			<div class=\"w-1/2 pr-2\">Having abilities in Parkour is only a part of the equation. Being an effective coach is a completely separate requirement of the role.</div>\r\n			<div class=\"w-1/2 pl-2\">Teaching is a skill. Our coaches have decades of experience, exposure and a certified education in coaching.</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>'),(111563,1494,'_builder_instance_6_organism_3_raw_code','field_60409dff3f7c0_field_5ffc51b1bf53e'),(111564,1494,'builder_instance_6_organism_4_enabled','1'),(111565,1494,'_builder_instance_6_organism_4_enabled','field_60409dff3f7c0_field_6010089610206'),(111566,1494,'builder_instance_6_organism_4_label','Why?'),(111567,1494,'_builder_instance_6_organism_4_label','field_60409dff3f7c0_field_6040a091892c1'),(111568,1494,'builder_instance_6_organism_4_raw_code','<div class=\"block w-full md:w-1/2 rounded pl-4 md:pl-10 mb-4 md:mb-10 relative\">\r\n	<div class=\"bg-ghost h-full text-black p-4 md:p-10 rounded fill-Emerald400\">\r\n		<div class=\"text-Emerald400\">Why?</div>\r\n		<svg class=\"absolute w-8 h-20 top-0 md:top-4 right-4 md:right-10 svg-inherit\">\r\n			<use xlink:href=\"#glyph-rectangles\"></use>\r\n		</svg>\r\n		\r\n		[[picture class=\"lazyload object-scale-down mx-auto h-60 md:h-80 lg:h-96\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/Essential/Cutouts/Lizzie_Slide.png\" alt=\"Lizzy does a slide monkey vault.\"]]\r\n				\r\n		<div class=\"text-3xl pt-2 border-t-2 pb-6\">For the Love</div>\r\n		<div class=\"flex items-stretch\">\r\n			<div class=\"w-1/2 pr-2\">Our passion for parkour shows in our sessions. We want to help others move, just as we do.</div>\r\n			<div class=\"w-1/2 pl-2\">Why do we teach? Simple - For the love of movement, self improvement and to build better humans.</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>'),(111569,1494,'_builder_instance_6_organism_4_raw_code','field_60409dff3f7c0_field_5ffc51b1bf53e'),(111570,1494,'builder_instance_6_organism_5_enabled','1'),(111571,1494,'_builder_instance_6_organism_5_enabled','field_60409dff3f7c0_field_6010089610206'),(111572,1494,'builder_instance_6_organism_5_label','Leading'),(111573,1494,'_builder_instance_6_organism_5_label','field_60409dff3f7c0_field_6040a091892c1'),(111574,1494,'builder_instance_6_organism_5_raw_code','<div class=\"block w-full md:w-1/2 rounded pl-4 md:pl-10 mb-4 md:mb-10 relative\">\r\n	<div class=\"bg-ghost h-full text-black p-4 md:p-10 rounded fill-Emerald400\">\r\n		<div class=\"text-Emerald400\">Take the Lead.</div>\r\n		<svg class=\"absolute w-8 h-20 top-0 md:top-4 right-4 md:right-10 svg-inherit\">\r\n			<use xlink:href=\"#glyph-left-right\"></use>\r\n		</svg>\r\n				\r\n		[[picture class=\"lazyload object-scale-down mx-auto h-60 md:h-80 lg:h-96\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/Essential/Cutouts/Kevin_Fly.png\" alt=\"Kevin Flies towards the camera.\"]]\r\n				\r\n		<div class=\"text-3xl pt-2 border-t-2 pb-6\">Leading by Example</div>\r\n		<div class=\"flex items-stretch\">\r\n			<div class=\"w-1/2 pr-2\">All of our coaches train regularly and often. We\'ll make sure we can demonstrate everything we plan as possible and reasonable.</div>\r\n			<div class=\"w-1/2 pl-2\">Knowing how to do something and doing it can be wildly different. We always lead our classes and sessions by example... Making sure we can do everything we\'re asking you to do.\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>'),(111575,1494,'_builder_instance_6_organism_5_raw_code','field_60409dff3f7c0_field_5ffc51b1bf53e'),(111576,1494,'builder_instance_6_organism_6