der_instance_2_organism_1_enabled','1'),(118401,1512,'_builder_instance_2_organism_1_enabled','field_60409dff3f7c0_field_6010089610206'),(118402,1512,'builder_instance_2_organism_1_label','The Service - Open Group'),(118403,1512,'_builder_instance_2_organism_1_label','field_60409dff3f7c0_field_6040a091892c1'),(118404,1512,'builder_instance_2_organism_1_raw_code','<div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-stretch py-4 md:py-10 pr-4 md:pr-10 \">'),(118405,1512,'_builder_instance_2_organism_1_raw_code','field_60409dff3f7c0_field_5ffc51b1bf53e'),(118406,1512,'builder_instance_2_organism_2_enabled','1'),(118407,1512,'_builder_instance_2_organism_2_enabled','field_60409dff3f7c0_field_6010089610206'),(118408,1512,'builder_instance_2_organism_2_label','The Service - Officer Training'),(118409,1512,'_builder_instance_2_organism_2_label','field_60409dff3f7c0_field_6040a091892c1'),(118410,1512,'builder_instance_2_organism_2_raw_code','<div class=\"block w-full md:w-1/2 rounded pl-4 md:pl-10 mb-4 md:mb-10 relative\">\r\n	<div class=\"bg-ghost h-full text-black p-4 md:p-10 rounded fill-black\">\r\n		<div class=\"text-black\">Entry Requirements.</div>\r\n		<svg class=\"absolute w-8 h-20 top-0 md:top-4 right-4 md:right-10 svg-inherit\">\r\n			<use xlink:href=\"#glyph-triangles\"></use>\r\n		</svg>\r\n				\r\n		[[picture class=\"lazyload object-scale-down mx-auto h-60 md:h-80 lg:h-96\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/Essential/Cutouts/Kevin_Step_Vault.png\" alt=\"Kevin does a step vault.\"]]\r\n				\r\n		<div class=\"text-3xl pt-2 border-t-2 pb-6\">Officer Training</div>\r\n		<div class=\"flex items-stretch\">\r\n			<div class=\"w-1/2 pr-2\">Learn the most effective ways to overcome troublesome obstacles and routes.</div>\r\n			<div class=\"w-1/2 pl-2\">Many future army officers, recruits and soldiers applying to other units or regiments have had private one-to-one sessions with londonparkour to help accomplish physical parts of the entry processes and training.</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>'),(118411,1512,'_builder_instance_2_organism_2_raw_code','field_60409dff3f7c0_field_5ffc51b1bf53e'),(118412,1512,'builder_instance_2_organism_3_enabled','1'),(118413,1512,'_builder_instance_2_organism_3_enabled','field_60409dff3f7c0_field_6010089610206'),(118414,1512,'builder_instance_2_organism_3_label','The Service - Infiltration / Exfiltration'),(118415,1512,'_builder_instance_2_organism_3_label','field_60409dff3f7c0_field_6040a091892c1'),(118416,1512,'builder_instance_2_organism_3_raw_code','<div class=\"block w-full md:w-1/2 rounded pl-4 md:pl-10 mb-4 md:mb-10 relative\">\r\n	<div class=\"bg-ghost h-full text-black p-4 md:p-10 rounded fill-black\">\r\n		<div class=\"text-black\">Entry & Exit.</div>\r\n		<svg class=\"absolute w-8 h-20 top-0 md:top-4 right-4 md:right-10 svg-inherit\">\r\n			<use xlink:href=\"#glyph-hoops\"></use>\r\n		</svg>\r\n				\r\n		[[picture class=\"lazyload object-scale-down mx-auto h-60 md:h-80 lg:h-96\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/Essential/Cutouts/Lizzie_rope_climb.png\" alt=\"Lizzy climbs up a rope.\"]]\r\n				\r\n		<div class=\"text-3xl pt-2 border-t-2 pb-6\">Infiltration & Exfiltration</div>\r\n		<div class=\"flex items-stretch\">\r\n			<div class=\"w-1/2 pr-2\">Route planning & parkour vision - Learn how to see the world as a challenge and understand what you are physically able to do.</div>\r\n			<div class=\"w-1/2 pl-2\">Assess potential routes from a distance with the fore-thought of being able to exfiltrate too. Be able to adapt at the moment and understand the factors involved with buildering and climbing techniques.</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>'),(118417,1512,'_builder_instance_2_organism_3_raw_code','field_60409dff3f7c0_field_5ffc51b1bf53e'),(118418,1512,'builder_instance_2_organism_4_enabled','1'),(118419,1512,'_builder_instance_2_organism_4_enabled','field_60409dff3f7c0_field_6010089610206'),(118420,1512,'builder_instance_2_organism_4_label','The Service - Penetration Testing'),(118421,1512,'_builder_instance_2_organism_4_label','field_60409dff3f7c0_field_6040a091892c1'),(118422,1512,'builder_instance_2_organism_4_raw_code','<div class=\"block w-full md:w-1/2 rounded pl-4 md:pl-10 mb-4 md:mb-10 relative\">\r\n	<div class=\"bg-ghost h-full text-black p-4 md:p-10 rounded fill-black\">\r\n		<div class=\"text-black\">Facility Test.</div>\r\n		<svg class=\"absolute w-8 h-20 top-0 md:top-4 right-4 md:right-10 svg-inherit\">\r\n			<use xlink:href=\"#glyph-left-right\"></use>\r\n		</svg>\r\n				\r\n		[[picture class=\"lazyload object-scale-down mx-auto h-60 md:h-80 lg:h-96\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/Essential/Cutouts/Ben_Jumps.png\" alt=\"Ben does a big standing broad jump.\"]]\r\n				\r\n		<div class=\"text-3xl pt-2 border-t-2 pb-6\">Penetration Testing</div>\r\n		<div class=\"flex items-stretch\">\r\n			<div class=\"w-1/2 pr-2\">Assessing the potential of bypassing physical security measures. We will help you understand the capabilities of the human body. Can an unauthorised person scale a security wall? Access a roof? Go where they\'re not meant to? Bypass the razor fence? Climb a building?</div>\r\n			<div class=\"w-1/2 pl-2\">All of these types of things are what our parkour professionals can help you assess. We\'ll be able to show you what is possible and what is not possible. We\'ll be able to give suggestions on how to protect and secure your facility better.</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>'),(118423,1512,'_builder_instance_2_organism_4_raw_code','field_60409dff3f7c0_field_5ffc51b1bf53e'),(118424,1512,'builder_instance_2_organism_5_enabled','1'),(118425,1512,'_builder_instance_2_organism_5_enabled','field_60409dff3f7c0_field_6010089610206'),(118426,1512,'builder_instance_2_organism_5_label','The Service - Strength & Conditioning'),(118427,1512,'_builder_instance_2_organism_5_label','field_60409dff3f7c0_field_6040a091892c1'),(118428,1512,'builder_instance_2_organism_5_raw_code','<div class=\"block w-full md:w-1/2 rounded pl-4 md:pl-10 mb-4 md:mb-10 relative\">\r\n	<div class=\"bg-ghost h-full text-black p-4 md:p-10 rounded fill-black\">\r\n		<div class=\"text-black\">Body Armour.</div>\r\n		<svg class=\"absolute w-8 h-20 top-0 md:top-4 right-4 md:right-10 svg-inherit\">\r\n			<use xlink:href=\"#glyph-rectangles\"></use>\r\n		</svg>\r\n				\r\n		[[picture class=\"lazyload object-scale-down mx-auto h-60 md:h-80 lg:h-96\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/Essential/Cutouts/Andy_pushups.png\" alt=\"Andy Does Pushups on his fingers.\"]]\r\n				\r\n		<div class=\"text-3xl pt-2 border-t-2 pb-6\">Strength & Conditioning</div>\r\n		<div class=\"flex items-stretch\">\r\n			<div class=\"w-1/2 pr-2\">We have no equipment in parkour. Just a pair of trainers. The idea is that the world around us is our gym and most training can be accomplished with simple things like a wall, a fence, a rail, or even nothing at all. </div>\r\n			<div class=\"w-1/2 pl-2\">We can show you how practical movement training is completely different from all other training because we\'re doing the exact movement required to overcome that challenge. Conditioning is the key here.\r\nConditioning parkour movements for power, strength, control and all other attributes are what keeps your training fun, enjoyable and easy to implement.</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>'),(118429,1512,'_builder_instance_2_organism_5_raw_code','field_60409dff3f7c0_field_5ffc51b1bf53e'),(118430,1512,'builder_instance_2_organism_6_enabled','1'),(118431,1512,'_builder_instance_2_organism_6_enabled','field_60409dff3f7c0_field_6010089610206'),(118432,1512,'builder_instance_2_organism_6_label','The Service - Close group'),(118433,1512,'_builder_instance_2_organism_6_label','field_60409dff3f7c0_field_6040a091892c1'),(118434,1512,'builder_instance_2_organism_6_raw_code','</div>'),(118435,1512,'_builder_instance_2_organism_6_raw_code','field_60409dff3f7c0_field_5ffc51b1bf53e'),(118436,1512,'builder_instance_2_organism','a:7:{i:0;s:7:\"rawcode\";i:1;s:7:\"rawcode\";i:2;s:7:\"rawcode\";