1_content','<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Thanks for emailing us!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">You might want to check the <a href=\"http://dev.londonparkour.com/support/\">wiki</a> first, because most things are answered there and you\'ll probably get you query answered quicker.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Top 5 common questions:</h4>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://londonparkour.com/classes/\">Classes</a> are listed on the class page. Please check for up-to-date schedule, times and days.</li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://londonparkour.com/privatesessions/\">Private Sessions</a>. Generally held on Mon / Tue / Sat / Sun before and after classes. Dependant on numbers of participants, time and location. We\'ll email you back with more details!</li>\r\n 	<li>What to wear &amp; bring? Normal gym clothing that you\'re happy to get dirty. Bring water but travel light. Sensible warm jackets for weather. However, we never use gloves.</li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://londonparkour.com/pt/\">PT Sessions</a>. We run normal strength &amp; conditioning, programming, nutrition and practical / function physical training too. Location / time / day all to be discussed and decided with you.</li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://londonparkour.com/class-locations/\">Class Locations</a>. Canada Water (indoors), Canada Water (outdoors), Oval (outdoors) and Deptford (mixed).</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 58px; text-align: left;\">If you want to know our current news, the Instagram channel <a href=\"http://instagram.com/london_parkour\">http://instagram.com/london_parkour</a> is where we post.</p>'),(133882,1640,'_form_emails_1_content','field_form_email_content'),(133883,1640,'form_emails','2'),(133884,1640,'_form_emails','field_form_emails'),(133885,1640,'form_editing_type',''),(133886,1640,'_form_editing_type','field_form_editing_type'),(133887,1640,'form_slack','0'),(133888,1640,'_form_slack','field_form_slack'),(133889,1640,'form_mailchimp','0'),(133890,1640,'_form_mailchimp','fie